<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عُمَرُ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْفَجْرُ الَّذِي كَأَنَّهُ ذَهَبُ السِّرْحَانِ»</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«ذَلِكَ السَّاطِعُ فِي السَّمَاءِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>